<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p><span><strong>生日快乐！</strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong>深情地说一句：</strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong>“我爱你，中国！”</strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201001/18ff98aa338044aebbafd014c42336e4.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>我们不忘</span></p>
<p><span>万千烈士的前仆后继</span></p>
<p><span><strong>小米加步枪</strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong>穿草鞋、击风浪</strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong>不辞路险、远赴战场</strong></span></p>
<p><span>把生命留在了追寻民族独立的远方 </span></p>
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201001/21960be721954a7992d4da4c9acea93a.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>他们没能看到黎明的曙光</span></p>
<p><span><strong>但心中永存信仰</strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong>那是真理的力量</strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201001/959c590e5cbe48ab8018916d44f351e4.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>我们不忘</span></p>
<p><span>建设祖国的岁月沧桑</span></p>
<p><span>茫茫戈壁、浩瀚海疆</span></p>
<p><span><strong>挚爱祖国、忠于人民</strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong>是他们克服千难万险的力量</strong></span></p>
